Revision history for Pony

revision 0.0.6  2010-10-28
----------------------------
A few fixes for Pony::Objects.
Added crapy database interface (Pony::Db) and driver Pony::Db::Redis.
Started Pony::Orm.

revision 0.0.5  2010-10-27
----------------------------
Add C-style comments support in Pony::Objects.

revision 0.0.4  2010-10-15
----------------------------
Add dump function in Pony::Objects.

revision 0.0.3  2010-10-14
----------------------------
Add singleton support.

revision 0.0.2  2010-10-09
----------------------------
